{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43364-chunu-and-munu-read","title":"Chunu and Munu Read","description":"Chunu and Munu discover the joys of reading!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Stephanie  Wei"],"illustrators":["Abin  Shrestha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43364-chunu-and-munu-read"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101414/size3/027db7659010cd4302f65b21b02a5688.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101414/size6/027db7659010cd4302f65b21b02a5688.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79430/size6/8d518e26bd08caeb81468bb576b6afeb.jpg","text":"2/16","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79431/size6/f620e1b1cc5c52b9f34d65196eb022cb.jpg","text":"Chunu and Munu are reading in a library.\n\"Chunu, look at this boy spinning around. This picture is so nice!\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79432/size6/f800c6d54ca52a4363a5c78d50c2a547.jpg","text":"\"Munu, look at these red blossoming flowers.\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79433/size6/07d24e945fe6c9cac840577a043af151.jpg","text":"\"Chunu, look at these beautiful butterflies with different colored wings.\"","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79434/size6/51fb2413d79d286aacf2e49311b1caf5.jpg","text":"In the library, there are books with wonderful pictures here, there, and everywhere!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79435/size6/0b269baa25ad52ffc4a0b2dbe117ba6a.jpg","text":"\"Chunu, read this. It is a book filled with songs.\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79436/size6/3b31c1661e1ca9cf56a271b4844aadff.jpg","text":"\"Munu, please tell me a story.\"","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79437/size6/d778bd23151d422118ac2c70b33eff74.jpg","text":"\"Please tell me a story that touches the heart.\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79438/size6/2ee8337aa1543dd931a2d440fe66f68f.jpg","text":"\"Come Chunu, let’s sit together. You take one book, and I will take another one. Let us read together.\"","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79439/size6/ea187a91175b016f8622751e77a867e1.jpg","text":"\"Oh, what is this? A dog and a rabbit going to school!\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79440/size6/e57cd769678f5fb348e8a63a9fd92b28.jpg","text":"\"Look at this bear sitting on a chair! He has warm eyes.\"","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79441/size6/494ede2e10883870dced6bde4dd88d87.jpg","text":"\"I will tell you a story. Which one do you want to listen to? A story about a rabbit or a dog?\"","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79442/size6/2b62363320fd05371387bee7266477e4.jpg","text":"\"Tell me a story with lots of art and pictures.\"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79443/size6/4834a13bf41a4b03bae7f63c483ee801.jpg","text":"\"I’m so happy to be at the library. I will come here everyday to read books.\"","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79444/size6/6a40b17a351236b16fd635779b8f7f1d.jpg","text":"\"Chunu, let’s take some books home where we can also enjoy reading them. Books can be our friends. Let’s read books, let’s love books!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":191}}